h4><p role=3D"paragraph" class=3D"prismic-p text-base mt-3 lg:text-lg lg:mt=
-6">Cryptic crosswords are like normal crosswords, but the clues tend to in=
volve wordplay and also have very convoluted, intentionally confusing hints=
. If you=E2=80=99re doing a cryptic crossword, know that&nbsp;<a href=3D"ht=
